ITableColumnInfoSource
public class AAVSOFormatPhasePlotColumnInfoSource
extends AAVSOFormatRawDataColumnInfoSource

AAVSO format (file, database) table column information source for phase plot mode. This class exploits the knowledge that its base class's column indices are offset by one compared to its. Yes, this breaks encapsulation but promotes reuse and easier maintainability in a controlled manner.
